In this video we share the 10 most effective exercises to start with calisthenics. These exercises are perfect to get stronger in the basics of calisthenics. Despite building a strong calisthenics foundation, these exercises help every beginner to get used to most of the calisthencis movements. They are great for building muscle, increasing strength and improving mobility. All aspects are essential within calisthenics training.  Next to the exercises, we also share a complete beginner calisthenics workout plan. You can take a screenshot or find the routine in our Calisthenics Training App...
